# Normalize line endings to LF in the working tree on every platform. The GitHub
# Windows runners default to core.autocrlf=true, which would otherwise check out
# CRLF and break (a) the build-agents frontmatter parser (its regex expects
# `---\n`) and (b) the generated-file drift check (CRLF on disk vs LF output).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets must never be line-ending converted.
*.png binary
